Citation.sTitle: Densities and Viscosities of Binary Liquid Mixtures of 2-Butanone with Branched Alcohols at (293.15 to 313.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: Densities and viscosities of the binary mixtures of 2-butanone with 2-propanol, 2-methyl-1-propanol, 2-butanol, and 2-methyl-2-butanol were measured over the entire mole fractions at (293.15, 298.15, 303.15, 308.15, and 313.15) K. Using the experimental values of densities, excess molar volumes VE were calculated. The results were discussed in terms of molecular interactions.
